Version 1.0.0.pre:
  Pre-release for testing the incompatible library migration introduced in 0.3.

Version 0.3:
  Extracted `libambx` as the canonical library and application require path.
  Breaking change (intentional): removed the old alternate library require paths and legacy constants
  (`Lights`, `ProtocolDefinitions`, `LEFT_FAN`, `RIGHT_FAN`) in favor of
  `Ambx::Lights`, `Ambx::Fans`, and `Ambx::Protocol`.
  Fixed interface claim failures to return strict success or failure.
  Fixed light clearing to run once per close operation with multiple handles.

Version 0.2:
  Added patch from jaaps at xbmc.org forums.
  For configuration see: http://forum.xbmc.org/showthread.php?t=71912&page=2
